><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Hello Eric,</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">I hope you had satisfactory conversation with Edleman leather.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">I am confirming that JEE does not want the current leather installed in G2.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">This is the leather he would like installed:</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Chair fully covered in: Cashmere Calf, Marble CC23</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Piping just like current seat to be in: Free Range Pampas FR22.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Both from Edelman leather samples, he still is patient and feels this is between you and Edelman.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">The Gulfstream is located at Newark , Signature and will be there for your crew to remove the seats any time between now and Friday, May 11th. Our paint slot is Monday May 14 start date.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Please let me know when you can remove the seats and I will get aircraft to the paint shop by Friday night.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">We just returned from Paris , and will depart Wed night at 630pm to St. Thomas in Boeing.</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV>\n<DIV>\n<P class=MsoNormal><STRONG><B><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">let me know your thoughts?</SPAN></FONT></B></STRONG><FONT face=Arial color=black size=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"></SPAN></FONT></P>